title: Rotometal launches new cylinders - Labels and Labeling
summary: Rotometal has introduced lightweight aluminum magnetic cylinders for printing machines. These cylinders are easier to assemble and disassemble, have better product quality, and are more durable than traditional cylinders. They are also more energy-efficient and have a lower environmental impact.

title: SW-Motech Introduces New Accessories For The Ducati DesertX - RideApart.com
summary: SW-Motech has released a new line of accessories for the Ducati DesertX, designed to enhance protection, convenience, and maintenance. These accessories include crash bars, an engine guard, axle sliders, a water pump protector, a center stand, and a sidestand foot extender. The accessories are made from high-quality materials and are designed to integrate seamlessly with the Ducati DesertX.
